overview:
Prior to starting Numbers Insight, Jose worked as a manager at a large healthcare organization where he lead a team in charge of developing and supporting the systems that handle information exchange between health plans, clearing houses, and providers.

He was also key in architecting a claim pricing engine capable of processing over 600,000 transactions a day. He has also worked in places like Stellent (now part of Oracle) and Motorola where he designed and developed mission critical system used in public safety.
